query:
INSERT INTO pages (
    id,
    course_id,
    content,
    url_path,
    title,
    chapter_id,
    order_number,
    copied_from,
    content_search_language,
    page_language_group_id,
    hidden
  )
SELECT uuid_generate_v5($1, id::text),
  $1,
  content,
  url_path,
  title,
  uuid_generate_v5($1, chapter_id::text),
  order_number,
  id,
  content_search_language,
  page_language_group_id,
  hidden
FROM pages
WHERE (course_id = $2)
  AND deleted_at IS NULL
RETURNING id,
  content;
